title: Provides for the conducting of visual assessments by ophthalmic dispensers
summary: Relates to the practice of ophthalmic dispensing by ophthalmic dispensers pursuant to a visual assessment; provides that the commissioner of education shall establish educational and examination requirements to certify ophthalmic dispensers to practice visual assessment.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to the practice of ophthalmic dispensing
